keyMappings:
# Vimium
# lily58 split layout
map k scrollDown
map l scrollUp
map j scrollLeft
map ; scrollRight
map J goBack
map : goForward
map K previousTab
map L nextTab

map <down> scrollDown
map <up> scrollUp

map <c-down> nextTab
map <c-up> previousTab
map <c-left> goBack
map <c-right> goForward

map <c-d> duplicateTab
map <c-s-up> firstTab
map <c-s-down> lastTab

map \ Vomnibar.activateTabSelection
